\h BONUS \d

\uUSAGE\n
bonus name

\uDESCRIPTION\n
Give another player bonus experience points for outstanding roleplaying.
Provide as an argument the name of a character who has introduced themselves to you (via the "intro" command).

Note that you must be at least level 3 to use this command, and you can only give out a bonus once every 24 hours.

\uRULES\n
This command is for the express purpose of rewarding fellow players for outstanding roleplaying; it may not be used under any other circumstances. Misuse of this command is grounds for discipline including banishment from CurryMUD.
Please be discriminating and sensible.
